description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Yulenka purrs with a rating of 63, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 189, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, Nine Lives for East, Nine Lives for South, and 1 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80633-39914-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [189 Votes, Top 5% Score]
